                "subtree_start_index": 270,
                "subtree_end_index": 270,
                "nodes": []
              },
              {
                "title": "10.5 For all cleaning processes an assessment should be performed to determine the variable factors which influence cleaning effectiveness and performance, e.g. operators, the level of detail in procedures such as rinsing times etc. If variable factors have…",
